研究
一、學位論文
博士論文：植物遺傳資源及其相關之傳統知識的獲取與利益分享機制─從法律、經濟與實證研究之觀點來分析植物遺傳資源之議題(包括生物剽竊、生物勘探與智慧財產權) (Access and benefit-sharing regimes concerning the utilization of plant genetic resources and traditional knowledge regarding the use of plant genetic resources: using law, economics, and empirical methods to analyze plant genetic resources issues, including biopiracy, bioprospecting, and intellectual property) (詳見: http://hdl.handle.net/2142/16035)。

